Class TransactionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • TransactionManager
  • public class TransactionManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The TransactionManager class is the user interface class that handles inputs commands, outputs data, and messages. Commands should begin with OC, OS, OM, CC, CS, CM, DC, DS, DM, WC, WS, WM, PA, PD, PN, Q TransactionManager accounts for any bad input by catching exceptions and notifying the user
    Author:
    Joshua Atienza, Kyle Lee
